sequenceDiagram
    participant Orchestrator as FMS Guardrails<br/>Orchestrator
    participant Detector as Regex Detector<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant Registry as Built-in Pattern<br/>Registry
    participant Engine as Regex Engine<br/>(regex crate)

    Note over Orchestrator,Engine: Flow 1: Text Content Detection (Built-in Patterns)

    Orchestrator->>Detector: POST /api/v1/text/contents<br/>Content-Type: application/json<br/>{"contents": ["text..."], "detector_params": {"regex": ["email","ssn"]}}
    activate Detector

    Detector->>Registry: Lookup "email", "ssn"
    Registry-->>Detector: RegexDetection structs<br/>(compiled regex + metadata)

    loop For each content string
        loop For each pattern
            Detector->>Engine: regex_match(pattern, text)
            Engine-->>Detector: Match positions & spans
        end
    end

    Detector-->>Orchestrator: 200 OK<br/>[{"start":5,"end":25,"detection":"pii",<br/>"detection_type":"pii","text":"user@example.com"}]
    deactivate Detector

    Note over Orchestrator,Engine: Flow 2: Custom Pattern Detection

    Orchestrator->>Detector: POST /api/v1/text/contents<br/>{"contents": ["text..."], "detector_params": {"regex": ["\\d{3}-\\d{4}"]}}
    activate Detector

    Note over Detector: Custom regex compiled<br/>per-request (no registry lookup)

    Detector->>Engine: Compile & match custom regex
    Engine-->>Detector: Match results

    Detector-->>Orchestrator: 200 OK<br/>[{"start":0,"end":8,"detection":"custom",<br/>"detection_type":"custom","text":"555-1234"}]
    deactivate Detector

    Note over Orchestrator,Engine: Health Check

    Orchestrator->>Detector: GET /health
    Detector-->>Orchestrator: 200 OK "healthy"
